comRadiusClient.description: This is the Zhone module identifier for the Zhone Bonding module.

zhoneRadiusClient.name: zhoneRadiusClient
zhoneRadiusClient.description: Start of the Zhone RADIUS Client MIB.

zhoneRadiusClientTable.name: zhoneRadiusClientTable
zhoneRadiusClientTable.description: The ZhoneRadiusClientTable contains the information required to authenticate a user using the RADIUS protocol. One entry exists per RADIUS server.

zhoneRadiusClientEntry.name: zhoneRadiusClientEntry
zhoneRadiusClientEntry.description: An entry in the Zhone Radius Client table.

zhoneRadiusClientIndex.name: zhoneRadiusClientIndex
zhoneRadiusClientIndex.description: This index is used to group serveral RADIUS server description together. This index is used in various Zhone provisioning information to specify which group of entries to use for a specific task or purpose.

zhoneRadiusClientId.name: zhoneRadiusClientId
zhoneRadiusClientId.description: This index specifies the specific RADIUS server information into a group of entries. When this group is provisioned for a task, this index is the order in which the servers will be contacted by the client.

zhoneRadiusClientRowStatus.name: zhoneRadiusClientRowStatus
zhoneRadiusClientRowStatus.description: Entry row status for SNMP create-and-go operation.

zhoneRadiusClientServerName.name: zhoneRadiusClientServerName
zhoneRadiusClientServerName.description: Radius server host name or IP address.

zhoneRadiusClientUdpPortNumber.name: zhoneRadiusClientUdpPortNumber
zhoneRadiusClientUdpPortNumber.description: The destination UDP port number for RADIUS authentication packets when authenticating using this server.

zhoneRadiusClientSharedSecret.name: zhoneRadiusClientSharedSecret
zhoneRadiusClientSharedSecret.description: This is the shared secret used by the RADIUS client and server for authentication and packet encryption.

zhoneRadiusClientRetryCount.name: zhoneRadiusClientRetryCount
zhoneRadiusClientRetryCount.description: The number of times to retry a failed request before we rotate to the next server in the list.

zhoneRadiusClientRetryInterval.name: zhoneRadiusClientRetryInterval
zhoneRadiusClientRetryInterval.description: This is the minimum time (in seconds) the device will wait before asuuming an error occurred and the request is retried.
